title: Calculus: Solution to Finding Total Visible Surface of a Sphere
description: Probably there are similar iterations out there. I was excited when I came up with this calculus problem. At the same time, I happened to take calculus class so definitely it helped me solve this problem set. Took me 1-2 days to get the solution.

title: Comparison Study: Creating a Dashboard of ASEAN Counties' Performances
description:
Originally a course project, I decided to explore deeper by experimenting with the performance index.
I came up with pipeline and formula of how to rank regional countries. Though it's introducing some sorts of bias.
